sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Swagger
    participant SSO as Cloud SSO
    participant SvcC as Service C POST /nilai
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant Token as IaeTokenService
    participant SOAP as /soap/v1/audit
    participant MQ as /api/v1/messages/publish
    participant Board as RabbitMQ Board

    Client->>SSO: POST /api/v1/auth/token warga01
    SSO-->>Client: JWT RS256

    Client->>SvcC: POST /api/v1/nilai Bearer JWT + X-IAE-KEY
    SvcC->>SSO: GET /api/v1/auth/jwks
    SvcC->>SvcC: Verify JWT + cek role dosen/admin
    SvcC->>SvcC: Validasi input
    SvcC->>DB: INSERT nilai
    DB-->>SvcC: Record tersimpan

    SvcC->>Token: getValidToken()
    Token-->>SvcC: IAE_SSO_TOKEN
    SvcC->>SOAP: XML Audit TeamID=TIM-09 ActivityName=NilaiRecorded
    SOAP-->>SvcC: ReceiptNumber
    SvcC->>DB: UPDATE receipt_number

    SvcC->>MQ: Publish routing_key=nilai.recorded
    MQ->>Board: iae.central.exchange
    Board-->>Board: Badge nilai.recorded

    SvcC-->>Client: 201 receipt_number + event_published true
